restaurants.name: Pizzeria da 'Gino
restaurants.description: Pizzeria da 'Gino is an authentic Italian eatery known for its delicious pizzas and inviting atmosphere. With a rustic charm and the aroma of freshly baked pies, it's the perfect place to savor traditional Italian flavors in a warm and welcoming setting.

dish_list.description: A type of ramen made with a base of pork bone broth, served with wheat noodles, slices of pork belly, green onions, and often a soft boiled egg.

dish_list.name: Shrimp Tempura
dish_list.description: A Japanese dish where shrimp are coated in batter and deep fried until crispy.

restaurants.name: Me Prendí Fuego
restaurants.description: Me Prendì Fuego is a Mexican fast-food gem known for its fiery flavors and bold spices. With a vibrant and lively atmosphere, it's the perfect spot to indulge in authentic Mexican cuisine that's guaranteed to set your taste buds ablaze.

dish_list.description: This historic dish is one of our most popular varieties of tacos, with origins dating back to the 1920s and 30s and the arrival of Lebanese and Syrian immigrants to Mexico.
